{"tid":2331014,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【估地方】同阿媽兵分兩路去同一個好靚嘅目的地","createTime":"2020-12-18T12:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T10:14:42.000Z","uid":201027,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a12e0d429fc349994d771335858e56a690756531","tid":2331014,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">見早前有巴打出post估地方引晒個個做偵探咁好玩，我都試下出題玩下，但無獎㗎！</span><br />\n<br />\n1.某年暑假，我喺電腦前search緊機票，呢個地方唔算熱門，價錢可接受就即刻買咗，兩日後出發。點知阿媽好嬲，話我又粒聲唔出走咗去。於是我就再search多張機票同佢一齊去。<br />\n<br />\n2.由於我買嘅特價票已賣完，所以要幫阿媽買多張，但就要分開坐機去，兵分兩路。雖然路線唔同，但地球係圓嘅，停咗一個中途站，約廿個鐘後，兩母女就會重逢。<br />\n<br />\n3.我去轉機嗰邊，以前就好似係每日有航班去呢個目的地，但唔知幾時開始，大部分有飛去呢度嘅航空公司，都變咗季節性航班。但阿媽搭嗰邊就無嘅。<br />\n<br />\n4.當我同朋友講我去呢個目的地，佢地既羡慕又擔心：「嘩，正喎！不過成日聽嗰度好多_ _ _ _，好擔心你返唔返到㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n5.旅行就梗有風險嘅，或者我同阿媽都好彩啦，又或者係班損友道聽途說嚇我啫，我地兩母女不知玩得幾鬼開心！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我地住喺呢間酒店，好貴</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRVj6RW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRVj6RW.png&h=7bbabcd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.快樂不知時日過，無損無爛返香港！一個專門收集各國錢幣嘅朋友就問我有冇用剩嘅貨幣俾佢。哎呀，我竟然無！不過佢無嬲我。<br />\n<br />\n7.大約兩星期後，朋友開信箱收到一堆公司信、銀行信，差啲睇唔到中間夾咗張我寄俾佢嘅明信片。佢好開心話我知：「聽就有聽過呢個地方，但估唔到風景咁靚㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n8.兩手空空無買乜返嚟俾朋友做手信，但我相信佢地都會用過呢個地方出嘅嘢，只係平時無留意啫！<br />\n<br />\n阿媽好滿意今次旅程，咁唔知有冇巴絲知我講邊度呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd5eae6c13e3c9803b4ea12b981dc8baa07f233","tid":2331014,"uid":225380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eaaa7128214e4b67c0857a55a8ab44f830c040b","tid":2331014,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"我到底睇撚左啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿魯阿圖"},{"pid":"e806c5ba874637f69d3e9879ce2ebcbb056b68e1","tid":2331014,"uid":60808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"伊朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7897daa520a5292b6b8ebd56cf7fbf31cb58141","tid":2331014,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e806c5ba874637f69d3e9879ce2ebcbb056b68e1","tid":2331014,"uid":60808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"伊朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"eb947dc1eb55145f3060b48c9ea60328489aa825","tid":2331014,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1eaaa7128214e4b67c0857a55a8ab44f830c040b","tid":2331014,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"我到底睇撚左啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿魯阿圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c20bc819788eb501892a9934e8a9325291a614c","tid":2331014,"uid":225380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"睇緊cape town 嘅 golf hotel"},{"pid":"e0bd6b5cbf368a3c94c3f006cb7bcf3a6be0ccde","tid":2331014,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c20bc819788eb501892a9934e8a9325291a614c","tid":2331014,"uid":225380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"睇緊cape town 嘅 golf hotel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"慢慢玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffcb4deb3016165c75c1159ebd9ce63f2f1235e","tid":2331014,"uid":225380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0bd6b5cbf368a3c94c3f006cb7bcf3a6be0ccde","tid":2331014,"u